statistics.semantic_type: expected close date of the opportunity in the CRM pipeline
statistics.pattern_description: Values are in ISO 8601 calendar date format 'YYYY-MM-DD', all within a plausible future range for opportunity expected close dates. No leading zeros beyond standard date formatting, no alphabetic characters, and values are clearly not unique identifiers but business dates likely to repeat across rows.

statistics.semantic_type: annual recurring revenue potential amount in whole currency units (likely cents or dollars)
statistics.pattern_description: Numeric-only, 6-digit positive integers with no leading zeros; values resemble monetary/amount measures rather than IDs, and column name 'arr_potential' suggests ARR (Annual Recurring Revenue) potential metric.
